summary: 该插件用于检测IIS服务器是否存在CVE-2015-1635(MS15-034)远程代码执行漏洞，当攻击者发送特殊设计的HTTP请求时可能导致任意代码执行。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the IIS server has the CVE-2015-1635(MS15-034) remote code execution vulnerability, which may lead to arbitrary code execution when an attacker sends specially crafted HTTP requests.
